# Simple MTL File Example

newmtl BasicMaterial
Ka 0.2 0.2 0.2  # Ambient color
Kd 1.0 0.0 0.0  # Diffuse color (Red)
Ks 0.5 0.5 0.5  # Specular color
Ns 50           # Specular exponent (shininess)
d 1.0            # Dissolve (transparency; 1.0 is opaque)
illum 2          # Illumination model (2 is for specular highlights)

newmtl AnotherMaterial
Ka 0.2 0.2 0.2
Kd 0.0 1.0 0.0  # Diffuse color (Green)
Ks 0.5 0.5 0.5
Ns 50
d 1.0
illum 2